title: 3 Bed in SE Austin provides room in your budget to flourish
posting_body: ['Conveniently close to schools, local shopping, dining, and entertainment.', 'Location provides easy access to Interstate 35, making your commute a breeze.', 'Creatively designed with attractive amenities to enhance your lifestyle.', 'Features include hardwood or carpeted floors, walk-in closets, patio, ceiling fans, central air and heating, disability access, and washer and dryer connections.', 'Entertaining is easy in the gourmet kitchen with breakfast bar, dishwasher, gas range, microwave, and refrigerator.', 'And this deal gets sweeter with extra storage, tile backsplash, upgraded lighting fixtures, pantry, and stainless steel appliances.', 'We are also pet-friendly with no weight limit!', 'Beautiful landscaping, shimmering swimming pool, state-of-the-art fitness center, gated access, 24-hour courtesy patrol, covered parking, on-site maintenance, and we offer senior and military discounts.', 'Economize without compromise!', 'Text 2I0-355-7852', 'Christena Barry - Award Winning Locator & Realtor', 'Spirit Real estate Group', 'ID:  44', '*Pics show general property, not necessarily particular unit.', '*Prices, availability, & specials subject to change.']
